title: HOUR 3 - Dallas Cowboys, Mark Schlereth
itunes:title: HOUR 3 - Dallas Cowboys, Mark Schlereth
description:
In hour 3, Nick recaps his thoughts on Tom Brady's return to Foxborough. Dallas may have the best team since Dak's rookie season anchored by a stout Defense. Mark Schlereth joins to Dallas Cowboys and the great moves they made in the off season and more.
